{"tid":1569501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【逆權運動】疑為撐警人士發「假收據」 港大宣佈暫停樊潔玲醫生職務","createTime":"2019-09-14T15:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T16:55:28.000Z","uid":51620,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15d8a60a56d7fc6ab33e534d379b8d345fc8c3c2","tid":1569501,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70523489_10158057985462448_7528789473287471104_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQkytpqEaLsH4PSl_ZFEYTT2Tpp8CvylXrVQW-5hjmBSaemqAMFx22hjQ2XvovGNapM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=46eb060870de29d2d27fc04269fe9122&amp;oe=5E059494\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70523489_10158057985462448_7528789473287471104_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQkytpqEaLsH4PSl_ZFEYTT2Tpp8CvylXrVQW-5hjmBSaemqAMFx22hjQ2XvovGNapM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D46eb060870de29d2d27fc04269fe9122%26oe%3D5E059494&h=429928c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淘大商場街坊日前（11日）聚集齊唱《願榮光歸香港》，結果發生不同意見市民衝突，今日大批手持中國旗人士到淘大商場「示威」，再次發生衝突，結果撐警毆打青年後，防暴警再出動拘捕青年，混亂間一名疑為站在支持政府和警方陣營的女士受傷送院，遺留一疊收據於現場，當中除了有一份保險公司的索賠申請表，同時亦有數張由醫生發出的收據，當中包括一張收據為下周一的收據。港大醫療系統發言人回應傳媒查詢時表示，留意到網上有指一名港大深圳醫院醫生發出懷疑虛假應診証明，已經要求港大深圳醫院院長即時暫停該名醫生的職務，並會就事件作出調查，以釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n該名女子送院後，現場遺留不少物品，未知是否與該名受傷女子有關。除了一些日常用品外，亦有一張署名為「Lam XXXXX」的保險索賠申請表，同時亦有多張由醫生「樊潔玲」發出的收據，收據顯示是由葵涌一間醫務所發出，而6張由醫生發出的收據中，每張均超過$1,000，其中一張收據更是於9月16日發出，收據銀碼同為$1,000，並獲得醫生親筆簽署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190914/60045403?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0VFcIAbOZQOdLjREe5jb50DxEHdUZ8dVJ-BNYb0U_N0SGoXwNIUAt0vJw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190914%2F60045403%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0VFcIAbOZQOdLjREe5jb50DxEHdUZ8dVJ-BNYb0U_N0SGoXwNIUAt0vJw&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=60ce6598\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190914%2F60045403%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0VFcIAbOZQOdLjREe5jb50DxEHdUZ8dVJ-BNYb0U_N0SGoXwNIUAt0vJw&h=d12fb559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190914/60045403?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0VFcIAbOZQOdLjREe5jb50DxEHdUZ8dVJ-BNYb0U_N0SGoXwNIUAt0vJw</a>"},{"pid":"4642731ceda9bb47da4a4a043557ee26b6930072","tid":1569501,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/lovepopolovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flovepopolovehk&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=761c73ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lovepopolovehk</a><br />\n藍絲戰線要人"},{"pid":"b6db4eb63fef96ef4a95452e3f0ce4859c2c47ed","tid":1569501,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"暫停咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa70d3f9a7a364959a7d3a3f4483c0f5344d9663","tid":1569501,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6db4eb63fef96ef4a95452e3f0ce4859c2c47ed","tid":1569501,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"暫停咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:55:28.000Z","msg":"好過冇"}]}